    "description": "真正的炼金术大师不仅需要原始的装饰品，还需要坐骑在坩埚之间移动得更快，以及为这些装饰品增加奖励的物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152890/extras/19fc9f51fbf64900825adef4503f06f5.webp?t=1663329143\" width=32 height=32 /></span>倾斜战斗头盔（永恒）<br><i>不仅是原始外观，还有有用的奖金。可以通过使用财富魔方分配 1 到 3 个随机属性来升级，然后使用无名魔方更改它们的值。</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152890/extras/a8578fd73ae6405c562730c75521b9d4.webp?t=1663329143\" width=32 height=32 /></span>有毒蒸汽锅炉（永恒）<br><i>这件珠宝充满了世界最遥远角落的阴暗奥秘。</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152890/extras/5430b59ffd04b67383337a9e9c045161.webp?t=1663329143\" width=32 height=32 /></span> 召唤盾背哨<br><i>使用时，召唤一个盾牌以加快移动速度。速度提高 70%。</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152890/extras/97e0324e099c873184ba512bce038f97.webp?t=1663329143\" width=32 height=32 /></span> 小幸运魔方<br><i>为永恒装饰头饰分配 1 个随机属性。分配属性的最大和最小可能值取决于角色的当前级别。</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152890/extras/73631d634c537797ba6732dba3a3b992.webp?t=1663329143\" width=32 height=32 /></span> 弱魔法羽毛<br><i>应用于背面附件并删除其临时限制。允许您获得随机模式（增益）。</i><br><br>购买此套装，您将获得超优惠的商品！",
